name: Super Duper pt5
description:
CONTROLS

  • ESC - quit
  • BACKSPACE - return to main menu
  • LEFT MOUSE - magic baby
  • A - move left
  • D - move right
  • W - move through gate
  • L - fullscreen

Take the leap with Steve as he attempts to climb to the top and let the world know just what he is!

Don't like some stats?  Think it is too hard?  Want to fight evil bananas??  Feel free to configure it however you like!

Hope you have some fun!
